title: HOUR 3 - Bucky Brooks, Kyle Shanahan

description:
In hour 3, Bucky Brooks joins to talk NFL, Trey Lance potential and more Dallas Cowboys. Colin also give his input on how impressive its been watching Kyle Shanahan turn non 1st round picks into viable players.
